@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_sadstn(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (0.25 * wp.abs(wp.abs(v0 + 0.68)))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.exp(wp.cos(v0 + 0.47)))
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.sin((tmp + 0.97 / v2 + 0.20)))
    tmp = tmp
    tmp = (v1 + 0.61)
    tmp = ((wp.abs(v1 + 0.25) - (v0 + 0.42 / v2 + 0.80)) * tmp)
    v1 = 0.79
    data[tid] = v0
